OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FA man accused of stabbing his wife to
OL,7,Fdeath while experiencing financial
OL,8,Fdifficulties has claimed she "took her
OL,9,Fown life", a court has heard.
OL,11,FEgyptian national Mohamed Samak has
OL,12,Fdenied killing Joanne Samak, 49, at
OL,13,Ftheir home in Droitwich Spa in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of July 1, 2024.
OL,16,FSamak, 42, was arrested by West Mercia
OL,17,FPolice after his alleged victim was
OL,18,Ffound at the address with what police
OL,19,Fdescribed as unsurvivable injuries.
