OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FOpening a trial at Worcester Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Tuesday, lead prosecutor Mr
OL,8,FHarpreet Sandhu KC told the jury that
OL,9,FSamak killed his wife after becoming
OL,10,Finterested in another woman and
OL,11,Fexperiencing financial difficulties.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor said Samak, who was a
OL,14,Fhockey coach who had previously worked
OL,15,Fwith the under-18 Welsh national team,
OL,16,Fhad "kept an eye" on his status as an
OL,17,Falleged beneficiary of Ms Samak's life
OL,18,Finsurance policy and pension.
OL,26,@xD@EOUxD@QO]
