OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FHis wife, who was to have begun
OL,7,Fworking at her new interior design
OL,8,Fbusiness on the day of her death, was
OL,9,Fsaid to be the "breadwinner" of the
OL,10,Fhousehold, and the defendant had been
OL,11,Fseeking the assistance of financial
OL,12,Fadvisers while struggling with his
OL,13,Fmental health, the court was told.
OL,15,FMr Sandhu told the jury that Samak had
OL,16,Fkilled his wife, but lied to police by
OL,17,Fclaiming she had instead "stabbed
OL,18,Fherself repeatedly" before he found
OL,19,Fher slumped on a bed with a knife in
OL,20,Fher stomach.
