OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FThe defendant alleged he had found Ms
OL,7,FSamak, who slept in a separate bedroom
OL,8,Ffrom her husband, at about 4.10am
OL,9,Fafter he woke to use the toilet, and
OL,10,Fimmediately phoned 999.
OL,12,FBut Mr Sandhu, who said a post-mortem
OL,13,Fexamination found six stab wounds on
OL,14,FMs Samak, including one to the chest,
OL,15,Faccused the defendant of later
OL,16,Fchanging his account "to fit the
OL,17,Fevidence".
