OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FDuring a police interview, Samak was
OL,7,Ftold neighbours had claimed to have
OL,8,Fheard screaming at about 3:00 am. He
OL,9,Ftold officers he was awoken by a noise
OL,10,Fcoming from the bathroom at about the
OL,11,Fsame time.
OL,13,FHe allegedly looked out from his
OL,14,Fbedroom, saw Ms Samak holding a knife,
OL,15,Fscreaming and "trying to stab
OL,16,Fherself", the court was told.
OL,18,FWhen he tried to help her, he said she
OL,19,Fwent into the bedroom and continued to
OL,20,Fstab herself before landing on the bed.
