OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FHe claimed to have waited an hour
OL,7,Fbefore calling the emergency services
OL,8,Fbecause he was crying and "struggling
OL,9,Fto breathe".
OL,11,FThe court heard that Samak, who moved
OL,12,Fto the UK after marrying Ms Samak in
OL,13,F2014, claimed his wife was struggling
OL,14,Fwith her mental health and alcohol at
OL,15,Fthe time of her death.
OL,17,FBut friends and family, including her
OL,18,Fbrother, Mark Vale, who gave evidence
OL,19,Fon Tuesday, denied this and said "she
OL,20,Fwas happy" and "loved her work" as an
OL,21,Finterior designer.
