OL,3,CMan who denies stabbing wife to death
OL,4,Cclaims she 'took her own life'
OL,6,FShe was also said to be "excited"
OL,7,Fabout her new business venture and was
OL,8,Fplanning a party and trip to Paris for
OL,9,Fher upcoming 50th birthday.
OL,11,FProsecutors said: "On the one hand,
OL,12,F(there is) a woman who had everything
OL,13,Fto live for, a woman who had made lots
OL,14,Fof future plans that decided to take
OL,15,Fher own life.
OL,17,F"Alternatively, her husband, who was
OL,18,Finterested in another woman, had
OL,19,Ffinancial concerns and had an eye on
OL,20,Fwhat he might get if she died, killed
OL,21,Fher."
